column2: SELECT u.up_col0 as col0, s.ra, s.dec, s.class, s.subClass, s.z, s.zErr, s.zWarning,s.bestObjID, s.specObjID, g.oiii_flux, g.oiii_flux_err, g.oiii_voff, g.oiii_chi2 FROM #upload u  JOIN #x x ON x.up_id = u.up_id  JOIN SpecObj s ON s.specObjID = x.specObjID  JOIN GalSpecLine AS g ON g.specObjID = s.specObjID&&&#', @log=#, @filter=#
